title: When using 'log in with google' on Omnivore, the website in popup breaks after logging into google
content:
On the Omnivore website, picking google as the login option causes a popup window to open. Logging into google in this window causes the contents of it to become white and unable to be interacted with, preventing logging in. Reopening the window opens it onto this white screen. Clearing cache opens it to the login screen, where the same problem repeats after logging in.

This problem still happened in troubleshooting mode
creator: joonasx
